headline.print_headline: Hiker,' Guru of Trails' Missing on Mount Rainier
headline.main: Hiker,' Guru of Trails' Missing on Mount Rainier

lead_paragraph: Crews searched Mount Rainier National Park on Friday for a prominent hiker and outdoors writer who was reported missing late Wednesday while she researched a story.
